Class Account

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.edgrantJBusRD.dbjson.Serializable
      • com.edgrantJBusRD.Account
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Serializable>
    public class Account
extends Serializable
    The Account class represents a user account in the transportation system. It stores information such as user name, email, password, account balance, and company affiliation.
